prodNameC: "鐳定" 醛類脂醇放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Aldosterone Maia Tracer: contains I-125 labelled Aldosterone derivative in phosphate buffer with bovine serum albumin
Aldosterone Maia Calibrators: contain respectively: 0-25-80-250-800-2500 pg/ml of aldosterone in human serum matrix with bovine serum albumin and sodium azide.
Aldosterone Maia Separation Reagent: contains goat anti-rabbit gammaglobulins coupled to magnetic particles in Tris buffer with bovine serum albumin and sodium azide.
Aldosterone Maia Antiserum: contains rabbit anti-aldosterone in aqueous solutions, bovine serum albumin and sodium azide.
Aldsteone Maia Diluent: contains lyophilized human serum matrix with sodium azide.
Serotest S: contains lyophilized control serum containing human serum with sodium azide.

applicantAddr: 台北市大同區承德路二段81號15樓
efficacy: 用來檢測血清、血漿、尿液中醛類脂醇的含量。
